    "en": {
      "name": "Red-Eyes Black Dragon Exceed",
      "effect": "\"Red-Eyes Black Dragon\" + 1 monster that mentions \"Dark Time Wizard\"\nMust be either Fusion Summoned, or Special Summoned (from your Extra Deck) by Tributing 1 face-up monster on either field during the turn a monster(s) was destroyed by the effect of \"Dark Time Wizard\". You can only Special Summon \"Red-Eyes Black Dragon Exceed\" once per turn this way, no matter which method you use. If this card is Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 Level 8 or lower monster from your hand or GY. Unaffected by your opponent's activated monster and Spell effects.",
